title: Cara Santana - Work Ethic, Secrets To Personal Brand Success, Traditional Vs Digital Talent & Hustle

description:
#161: On this episode we sit down with actress Cara Santana. Cara has built a brand as a digital influencer as well as an actor using the power of social media. She is also an entrepreneur who has built and sold a business. On this episode we discuss work ethic, secrets to personal brand success, traditional talent vs digital talent and hustle.
